
Steps

1 ) clone repo https://github.com/sooperset/mcp-atlassian

2) Create atlassian token

3) open cmd and run below commands, this will up mcp jira server
    $env:JIRA_URL="https://<ur-rul>>.atlassian.net"
    $env:JIRA_USERNAME="<mail-id>>@gmail.com"
    $env:JIRA_API_TOKEN="<token>"


    uvx mcp-atlassian --transport streamable-http --stateless --port 9000

refer: https://mcp-atlassian.soomiles.com/docs/http-transport#streamable-http



